snippet.title: Complex Numbers: Multiplying and Dividing in Polar Form, Ex 2
snippet.description: Thanks to all of you who support me on Patreon. You da real mvps!   $1 per month helps!! :)  https://www.patreon.com/patrickjmt !! Complex Numbers: Multiplying and Dividing in Polar Form, Ex 2. In this video, I give the formula for multiplication and division of two complex numbers that are in polar form.
